{"tid":1679610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重開) 我正式宣佈 11月2開始一連五日既各區開花示威","createTime":"2019-10-28T09:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T00:36:36.000Z","uid":133341,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd65087f36ec68e26dd7280720b06ca422f7c941","tid":1679610,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"眾所周知<br />\n好多港豬九龍打緊仗<br />\n佢地重係自己區飲飲食食<br />\n風花雪月<br />\n我覺得有需要開始一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有目標性</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有連續性</span></strong>既活動<br />\n針對<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港豬</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸遊客</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尋日打大戰<br />\n班大陸人係黃埔嘉里酒店上面食煙飲酒影大頭<br />\n個個係度笑鳩我地<br />\n我地唔可以再比佢地佔用我地既資源<br />\n重要笑返我地<br />\n旺角同東鐵重有好多大陸狗係度笑啊<br />\n要燒到去社區先得<br />\n九龍打仗<br />\n新界港島high tea 食buffet...<br />\n<br />\n我地要支持新模式<br />\n個運動係時候要有d模式變化<br />\n<br />\n重點係大陸狗同藍絲<br />\n就算唔打得郁得<br />\n最少都要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鬧下嚇下</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n重點目標<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">商場</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">酒店</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n商場<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">靜坐</span></strong><br />\n酒店<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">堵大門</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有無邊間深藍酒店集團list?<br />\n或者主要做大陸客既酒店??<br />\n黃埔嘉里首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先有共識<br />\n再定謀略<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n和勇不分<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"6bcce52dfe699f8945f4996ddc786d5f96b9bc7a","tid":1679610,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"fed306dd21e1ee26508fe125371a87682845defa","tid":1679610,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"搵大陸狗做肉盾啊!!!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686e2b98c63610cd7ec3679bba74d38abe8762d4","tid":1679610,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"我一早都話聽到普通話就係唔係吊鳩左佢先。不過吊之前最好問清楚<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">是否大陸人</span></strong></span>。一陣吊錯隔離馬拉台灣自己友就唔好啦。要對準目標係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8ed20b01765e00b04734a4bb0f62e5021f107aa5","tid":1679610,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"一 日拉2百個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe275991977ac580a67c019ae50960bc2f1f852c","tid":1679610,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"等人權法等於等運到<br />\n香港人唔僧坐以待斃"},{"pid":"a9b8a9a5ecd5e98049c10cba35fcf23df97d623f","tid":1679610,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"EU agrees to Brexit deadline extension up to 31 January 2020, says Donald Tusk"},{"pid":"c8c1ee6805ba8a91e35bba9a55a702cc968e8637","tid":1679610,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等人權法等於等運到<br />\n香港人唔<span style=\"color: red;\">會</span>坐以待斃</blockquote>"},{"pid":"983ac19931b553d5838b9136d7faa49e0d015bb4","tid":1679610,"uid":33875,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"但好多講香港話唔正既大媽阿叔企係我地呢邊，尋日旺角就見唔少，係到派水做哨，仲有上次太子黃絲大媽鬧走三毛鬼妹，去到現場邊有時間慢慢分邊個係大陸狗邊個係自己友。而且針對「飲飲食食」咪變咗「日本社運」個情況咁"},{"pid":"7401da2c8dc40e9f5b9428a79504f399d19010f2","tid":1679610,"uid":139190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n根本唔應該再淨係星期六日出黎示威<br />\npart time示威夠未啊?"},{"pid":"61e076c378b9c8c6debc0cd4c77d607e39a8acdf","tid":1679610,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7401da2c8dc40e9f5b9428a79504f399d19010f2","tid":1679610,"uid":139190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n根本唔應該再淨係星期六日出黎示威<br />\npart time示威夠未啊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:39:22.000Z","msg":"我都覺得星期六日既抗爭做唔到咩"},{"pid":"1c716e700252ecc6d7d4168b48e02dac3015828e","tid":1679610,"uid":224916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"686e2b98c63610cd7ec3679bba74d38abe8762d4","tid":1679610,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"我一早都話聽到普通話就係唔係吊鳩左佢先。不過吊之前最好問清楚<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">是否大陸人</span></strong></span>。一陣吊錯隔離馬拉台灣自己友就唔好啦。要對準目標係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"唔好一聽到普通話就屌，其實某部份大陸人其實係為左睇真相去到示威現場的，呢班人好珍貴，我地成日想將革命火種燒返大陸就係靠佢地<br />\n<br />\nd on99既大陸人坦白講都唔夠膽去現場啦<br />\n<br />\n然後就係香港係有唔少台灣旅客架，台灣係我地盟友黎，唔好搞到人地國民，同有Ｄ韓國人普通話都唔錯"},{"pid":"492a5e05cf0016b683521e54b6f5f581f011369b","tid":1679610,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c716e700252ecc6d7d4168b48e02dac3015828e","tid":1679610,"uid":224916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"686e2b98c63610cd7ec3679bba74d38abe8762d4","tid":1679610,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"我一早都話聽到普通話就係唔係吊鳩左佢先。不過吊之前最好問清楚<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">是否大陸人</span></strong></span>。一陣吊錯隔離馬拉台灣自己友就唔好啦。要對準